race.comment: BAROSKI (1) was a sharp 28.84 winner of a OPEN at this track last start. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. JIMMY ROO (2) comes off a (28.81) win last time, scoring by 3.5 lengths in a OPEN over 498m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. SHE'S SAINTLY (5) is a promising dog in the frame at four of nine starts including four wins and was a last start winner (28.78) over 498m at this track. Tends to go well on this box draw. Rates a winning chance on best. COOL BANANAS (4) was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.
